          </div>
          <div class="stacked" tyle="padding-bottom:15px">
            <span class="readable">&ldquo;As Nietzsche said, “If we have our own ‘why’ of life, we shall get along with any ‘how.&rdquo;</span>
            <nobr>
              &mdash;
